<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20432484">怎样的旅行才称得上「会玩」？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="353376" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">最近看到这篇文章：为什么中国盛产游客却最不会玩？ <a href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_490075660102dxio.html?tj=1#" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog</span><span class="invisible">_490075660102dxio.html?tj=1#</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a><br>那么，怎么样才称得上「会玩」呢？</div>


